<br>
Also you can be a thief / treasure hunter oriented character that deciphers treasure maps and takes groups out to dig it up (they'll have to kill the monsters that appear though).<br>
<br>
In all the other games out now I think you still have to fight stuff to advance (Asheron's call, Dark Age of Camelot, etc)<br>
